snippet: The CME Group, the giant Chicago exchange, sued its regulator late Thursday over a new rule that aims to shed light on the derivatives market in the latest legal assault on the Dodd-Frank regulatory overhaul.

headline.main: Regulator Faces Another Lawsuit Over Dodd-Frank
